CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Tableau - The Physical Activities Department of the YMCA staged a series of exhibitions at the anniversary celebration last Thursday. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boys wearing shorts and metallic paint, performing basketball exhibition on small stage in gymnasium interior for YMCA anniversary celebration, audience seated at tables in foreground
